item.title: CVE-2023-33989|2024-08-02T15:54:14.322Z -- sap_se -- sap%20netweaver%20%28bi%20cont%20add%20on%29
item.description: An attacker with non-administrative authorizations in SAP NetWeaver (BI CONT ADD ON) - versions 707, 737, 747, 757, can exploit a directory traversal flaw to over-write system files. Data from confidential files cannot be read but potentially some OS files can be over-written leading to system compromise.
